research/history/logs/agent_round_0050.stdout.log:1851:research/history/logs/agent_round_0049.stdout.log:1521:research/history/logs/agent_round_0044.stdout.log:451:research/history/results.tsv:36:r35_1774721279	1774721279	ok	discard	0.13181091845035553	128	lowrank_expert_topk	1				/root/sparsify-ascend/checkpoints/research_agent/round_0035/round0035_standard_1774721005_dp2_bs1_ga8_ef1_k128_20260329_020331	3ddd5ec8893e603c60b8e43d16e29e26e249a695			已实现并 smoke 通过新的 `lowrank_expert_topk` family，用最小 lowrank+expert 原型覆盖当前高优先级未验证结构槽位。建议下一轮以 r12(topk K=128 EF=1) 为参考，只切换到 `ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_expert_topk`，先在约 0.56x total_cost 的低开销带验证该 family 是否能形成新的 Pareto 段。	这轮只改了一个 env 参数 `ARCHITECTURE`，相对 r12 保持 K=128、EF=1、LR=8e-4、optimizer=adam 不变，归因清晰。代码侧只做最小 family 原型接线，没有引入新 tunable，因此不存在 override/runner 静默回退风险。风险是当前 prototype 的 expert 数和 active_experts 仍是固定值，若首轮效果一般，不能立刻下结论否定 `lowrank + expert` 方向本身。	/root/sparsify-ascend/research/history/logs/round0035_standard_1774721005.log
research/history/logs/agent_round_0050.stdout.log:1852:research/history/logs/agent_round_0049.stdout.log:1522:research/history/logs/agent_round_0044.stdout.log:452:research/history/results.tsv:37:r36_1774721605	1774721605	ok	discard	0.14529234170913696	160	lowrank_expert_topk	1				/root/sparsify-ascend/checkpoints/research_agent/round_0036/round0036_standard_1774721421_dp2_bs1_ga8_ef1_k160_20260329_021027	5efdcd36d7723170881d89edc581d7e56d7cdf0a			继续验证新 family `lowrank_expert_topk`，不回到 old-family 微调。以 r35 为参考只提高 `K` 到 160，在仍低于当前最佳可行点 0.75x 总成本的前提下，检查 lowrank trunk + local expert residual 是否开始形成比 `expert_topk` 更有竞争力的中低成本 Pareto 斜率。	满足单轮单变量约束；相对 r35 仅修改 `K`。这是对刚引入的新结构做最小必要的第二个锚点，而不是回到 plain selector 的局部扫点。按当前成本估算，`lowrank_expert_topk, EF=1, K=160` 的 total_cost 约 0.69x，仍在预算内，且能直接回答该 family 是否具有继续扩展价值。	/root/sparsify-ascend/research/history/logs/round0036_standard_1774721421.log
