ANK`/`STAGE1_RATIO`，应同时补齐该 architecture 在 override registry 中的允许键，避免后续 param_only 回合静默拒绝 override。"],"touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py","research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py"]}
