research/history/logs/agent_round_0046.stdout.log:284:{"decision": "discard", "status": "ok", "timestamp": "1774726962", "val_fvu": "0.13398849964141846", "observed_fvu": "0.133988", "k": "192", "architecture": "lowrank_expert_residual", "expansion_factor": "1", "run_health": "normal", "termination_reason": "completed", "tokens_per_sec": "111050.442528", "baseline_ratio": "0.999997", "checkpoint": "/root/sparsify-ascend/checkpoints/research_agent/round_0044/round0044_standard_1774726598_dp2_bs1_ga8_ef1_k192_20260329_033644", "experiment_id": "r44_1774726962", "head_commit": "714f30bebc5ce67f4f908916851616176769e69f", "description": "Round 43 的 `lowrank_expert_topk` 被 policy 的 behavioral-diff blocker 拦截，这一轮先不把预算继续投到被运行时策略卡住的 family，而是沿当前最强且已验证兼容的 `lowrank_expert_residual` 继续向低成本带延伸。以 r37 为参考仅下调 `TRUNK_RANK` 到 16，预计把总成本从约 1.06x 压到约 0.52x，直接回答这条三段式结构在接近 0.5x 区域是否还能保持明显优于现有低成本 anchor 的质量。", "self_review": "满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r37 只改 `TRUNK_RANK`。这不是旧 family 的局部 K 轴打磨，而是在当前主线结构上做一次高信息量的成本压缩试验；相比继续追 `lowrank_expert_topk`，它避免再次撞上已知 policy blocker。风险是 `TRUNK_RANK=16` 比 r38 的 128 更激进，FVU 可能明显恶化；但这正是本轮要回答的核心问题，即 lowrank+expert+residual 在接近 0.5x 带时是否仍然成立。", "log_path": "/root/sparsify-ascend/research/history/logs/round0044_standard_1774726598.log", "metrics_path": "/root/sparsify-ascend/checkpoints/research_agent/round_0044/round0044_standard_1774726598_dp2_bs1_ga8_ef1_k192_20260329_033644/metrics.jsonl", "curve_start_fvu": "0.165712", "curve_mid_fvu": "0.149947", "curve_end_fvu": "0.133988", "curve_late_slope": "-0.000000", "curve_still_improving": "true", "initial_target_tokens": "30000000", "final_target_tokens": "50000000", "final_total_tokens": "49979392", "resume_stage_count": "3", "continuation_stop_reason": "plateau", "continued_from_checkpoint": "true"}
research/history/logs/agent_round_0036.stdout.log:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","family_name":"lowrank_expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","reference_round":35,"env_overrides":[{"key":"K","value":"160"}],"expected_win":"lower_fvu","needs_sanity":false,"hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_{e(x)}(x)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}。其中 U={u_r} 是静态 low-rank trunk 向量库，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库；在线侧先计算 trunk 系数 β_r(x)，再用轻量 router 选择单个静态 expert 子库 e(x)，并只在该子库内做 local top-k 得到 α_{e,i}(x)。因此它可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路，兼容性判定为扩展兼容。相对 r35 仅改 K: 128 -> 160，回答一个结构问题：在 lowrank+expert 这个新 family 中，适度增加 sparse residual 容量后，FVU 是否会比 plain expert_topk 的同成本邻域下降更快，从而证明 trunk+expert 组合值得继续推进。","summary":"继续验证新 family `lowrank_expert_topk`，不回到 old-family 微调。以 r35 为参考只提高 `K` 到 160，在仍低于当前最佳可行点 0.75x 总成本的前提下，检查 lowrank trunk + local expert residual 是否开始形成比 `expert_topk` 更有竞争力的中低成本 Pareto 斜率。","self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束；相对 r35 仅修改 `K`。这是对刚引入的新结构做最小必要的第二个锚点，而不是回到 plain selector 的局部扫点。按当前成本估算，`lowrank_expert_topk, EF=1, K=160` 的 total_cost 约 0.69x，仍在预算内，且能直接回答该 family 是否具有继续扩展价值。","next_hypotheses":["如果 `lowrank_expert_topk K=160` 相对 r35 出现清晰 FVU 改善且斜率优于 `expert_topk`，下一轮仍保持 family 不变，只改 `K` 到 192，确认该 family 在 0.8x 附近是否继续沿 Pareto 前进。","如果 `K=160` 仍无明显收益，则应停止继续打磨该两段式原型，优先转向 `lowrank + expert + residual` 或 `two-stage residual expert`，而不是退回 plain `topk/jumprelu/factorized_topk`。"],"notes_to_memory":["`lowrank_expert_topk` 的 LUTurbo 形式是 trunk 静态库 + 单 expert 静态子库上的有限加权和，属于扩展兼容 family，不是动态字典。","当前已完成新 family 首轮验证；Round 36 只补第二个 K 锚点，目标是判断 lowrank+expert 的 FVU-cost 斜率，而不是刷新全局最低 FVU。","成本估算：`lowrank_expert_topk, EF=1, K=160` 约为 total 0.69x（selection 0.22x + deployment 0.47x），显著低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束，也低于当前最佳可行点 0.75x。","若该点仍弱，应把后续结构预算转向三段式 `lowrank + expert + residual` 或 `two-stage residual expert`。"],"touched_files":[]}
