research/history/logs/agent_round_0044.stdout.log:527:research/history/round_summaries/round_0042.json:19:    "hypothesis": "\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u8bbe\u4e3a x_hat = \u03a3_{r=1..R} \u03b2_r(x) u_r + \u03a3_{i\u2208S_{e(x-t(x))}(x-t(x))} \u03b1_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}\uff0c\u5176\u4e2d t(x)=\u03a3_{r=1..R} \u03b2_r(x) u_r\u3002\u4e5f\u5c31\u662f\u5148\u7528\u9759\u6001 low-rank trunk \u5411\u91cf\u5e93 U={u_r} \u91cd\u6784\u5e73\u6ed1\u4e3b\u5e72\uff0c\u518d\u5bf9\u6b8b\u5dee\u7528\u8f7b\u91cf router \u9009\u62e9\u5355\u4e2a\u9759\u6001 expert \u5b50\u5e93 B_e={b_{e,i}} \u5e76\u505a\u5c40\u90e8 sparse \u4fee\u6b63\uff1b\u56e0\u6b64\u5b83\u53ef\u76f4\u63a5\u5bfc\u51fa\u5230 LUTurbo/Lottable \u7684\u201ctrunk \u67e5\u8868 + expert \u5b50\u5e93\u67e5\u8868 + \u6709\u9650\u52a0\u6743\u548c\u201d\u63a8\u7406\u94fe\u8def\u3002\u517c\u5bb9\u6027\u5224\u65ad\uff1a`lowrank_expert_topk` \u5c5e\u4e8e\u6269\u5c55\u517c\u5bb9\u3002\u4e3b\u5047\u8bbe\u662f\uff1a\u76f8\u5bf9 r27 \u7684\u7eaf `expert_topk`\uff0c\u52a0\u5165\u8f7b\u91cf low-rank trunk \u540e\uff0c\u80fd\u663e\u8457\u6539\u5584\u91cd\u6784\u8d28\u91cf\uff0c\u5e76\u56de\u7b54 `lowrank + expert` \u8fd9\u6761\u9ad8\u4f18\u5148\u7ea7\u7ed3\u6784\u7ebf\u662f\u5426\u503c\u5f97\u7ee7\u7eed\uff0c\u5373\u4f7f\u9996\u70b9\u843d\u5728\u4e2d\u6210\u672c\u5e26\u4e5f\u6709\u4fe1\u606f\u4ef7\u503c\u3002",
research/history/logs/agent_round_0044.stdout.log:528:research/history/round_summaries/round_0042.json:20:    "summary": "\u4e0d\u56de\u5230 plain selector \u90bb\u57df\u5fae\u8c03\uff0c\u4e5f\u4e0d\u7ee7\u7eed\u5bf9\u672a\u77e5\u7ed3\u679c\u7684 `two_stage_residual_expert` \u505a\u9884\u8bbe\u8c03\u53c2\u3002\u672c\u8f6e\u4ee5 r27 \u7684 `expert_topk K=192 EF=1` \u4e3a matched baseline\uff0c\u53ea\u6539 `ARCHITECTURE` \u5230 `lowrank_expert_topk`\uff0c\u5148\u62ff\u5230 `lowrank + expert` \u8fd9\u6761\u7ed3\u6784\u7ebf\u5728\u5f53\u524d target \u4e0a\u7684\u9996\u4e2a\u771f\u5b9e\u8bad\u7ec3\u70b9\u3002",
research/history/logs/agent_round_0044.stdout.log:533:research/history/round_summaries/round_0042.json:40:      "\u5982\u679c `lowrank_expert_topk` \u9996\u70b9\u660e\u663e\u4f18\u4e8e r27 `expert_topk`\uff0c\u4e0b\u4e00\u8f6e\u4fdd\u6301 family \u4e0d\u53d8\uff0c\u53ea\u6539 `TRUNK_RANK` \u5411\u4f4e\u6210\u672c\u65b9\u5411\u538b\u7f29\uff0c\u6d4b\u8bd5\u662f\u5426\u80fd\u5f62\u6210\u65b0\u7684 Pareto \u6bb5\u3002",
research/history/logs/agent_round_0044.stdout.log:535:research/history/round_summaries/round_0042.json:61:    "description": "\u4e0d\u56de\u5230 plain selector \u90bb\u57df\u5fae\u8c03\uff0c\u4e5f\u4e0d\u7ee7\u7eed\u5bf9\u672a\u77e5\u7ed3\u679c\u7684 `two_stage_residual_expert` \u505a\u9884\u8bbe\u8c03\u53c2\u3002\u672c\u8f6e\u4ee5 r27 \u7684 `expert_topk K=192 EF=1` \u4e3a matched baseline\uff0c\u53ea\u6539 `ARCHITECTURE` \u5230 `lowrank_expert_topk`\uff0c\u5148\u62ff\u5230 `lowrank + expert` \u8fd9\u6761\u7ed3\u6784\u7ebf\u5728\u5f53\u524d target \u4e0a\u7684\u9996\u4e2a\u771f\u5b9e\u8bad\u7ec3\u70b9\u3002",
research/history/logs/agent_round_0044.stdout.log:574:research/history/round_summaries/round_0035.json:42:      "\u5728 target proxy(1024x4096) \u4e0a\uff0c`lowrank_expert_topk` \u7684\u4f30\u7b97\u6210\u672c\u4e3a\uff1aK=128 -> total 0.56x\uff1bK=160 -> total 0.69x\uff1bK=192 -> total 0.81x\u3002\u4f4e\u5f00\u9500\u8d77\u70b9\u5e94\u4f18\u5148\u4ece K=128 \u5f00\u59cb\u3002"
research/history/logs/agent_round_0044.stdout.log:609:research/history/logs/agent_action_0036.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","family_name":"lowrank_expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","reference_round":35,"env_overrides":[{"key":"K","value":"160"}],"expected_win":"lower_fvu","needs_sanity":false,"hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_{e(x)}(x)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}。其中 U={u_r} 是静态 low-rank trunk 向量库，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库；在线侧先计算 trunk 系数 β_r(x)，再用轻量 router 选择单个静态 expert 子库 e(x)，并只在该子库内做 local top-k 得到 α_{e,i}(x)。因此它可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路，兼容性判定为扩展兼容。相对 r35 仅改 K: 128 -> 160，回答一个结构问题：在 lowrank+expert 这个新 family 中，适度增加 sparse residual 容量后，FVU 是否会比 plain expert_topk 的同成本邻域下降更快，从而证明 trunk+expert 组合值得继续推进。","summary":"继续验证新 family `lowrank_expert_topk`，不回到 old-family 微调。以 r35 为参考只提高 `K` 到 160，在仍低于当前最佳可行点 0.75x 总成本的前提下，检查 lowrank trunk + local expert residual 是否开始形成比 `expert_topk` 更有竞争力的中低成本 Pareto 斜率。","self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束；相对 r35 仅修改 `K`。这是对刚引入的新结构做最小必要的第二个锚点，而不是回到 plain selector 的局部扫点。按当前成本估算，`lowrank_expert_topk, EF=1, K=160` 的 total_cost 约 0.69x，仍在预算内，且能直接回答该 family 是否具有继续扩展价值。","next_hypotheses":["如果 `lowrank_expert_topk K=160` 相对 r35 出现清晰 FVU 改善且斜率优于 `expert_topk`，下一轮仍保持 family 不变，只改 `K` 到 192，确认该 family 在 0.8x 附近是否继续沿 Pareto 前进。","如果 `K=160` 仍无明显收益，则应停止继续打磨该两段式原型，优先转向 `lowrank + expert + residual` 或 `two-stage residual expert`，而不是退回 plain `topk/jumprelu/factorized_topk`。"],"notes_to_memory":["`lowrank_expert_topk` 的 LUTurbo 形式是 trunk 静态库 + 单 expert 静态子库上的有限加权和，属于扩展兼容 family，不是动态字典。","当前已完成新 family 首轮验证；Round 36 只补第二个 K 锚点，目标是判断 lowrank+expert 的 FVU-cost 斜率，而不是刷新全局最低 FVU。","成本估算：`lowrank_expert_topk, EF=1, K=160` 约为 total 0.69x（selection 0.22x + deployment 0.47x），显著低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束，也低于当前最佳可行点 0.75x。","若该点仍弱，应把后续结构预算转向三段式 `lowrank + expert + residual` 或 `two-stage residual expert`。"],"touched_files":[]}
research/history/logs/agent_round_0044.stdout.log:641:research/history/logs/agent_action_0037.json:1:{"change_type":"edit_sae_code","command":"run","family_name":"lowrank_expert_residual","family_stage":"prototype","reference_round":27,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_expert_residual"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","needs_sanity":true,"hypothesis":"最终重构公式设为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_e(x)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i} + Σ_{j∈T(x)} γ_j(x) c_j。这里 U={u_r} 是静态 low-rank trunk 向量库，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库，C={c_j} 是静态 residual 补偿库；在线侧先计算 trunk 系数 β_r(x)，再用轻量 router 选择单个 expert 子库 e(x) 并在其内做局部 sparse 选择，最后对剩余残差再做一次小预算 sparse 补偿。因此它仍可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”流水线，兼容性判定为扩展兼容。主假设是：在与 r27 相同的 EF=1、K=192 recipe 下，把 `expert_topk` 升级为 `lowrank + expert + residual` 三段式结构，能回答‘仅有 lowrank+expert 仍不足时，加入第二段 residual 修正是否会形成新的结构性 Pareto 段’这个当前更关键的问题。","summary":"不继续在 `lowrank_expert_topk` 上做第三个邻域扫点，而是进入下一结构槽位：实现最小可运行的 `lowrank_expert_residual` 原型。以 r27 的 `expert_topk K=192 EF=1` 为 matched baseline，只改 `ARCHITECTURE`，先验证三段式结构本身是否值得继续。","self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束：运行配置相对 r27 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。这轮优先解决结构未知量，而不是继续在已显示弱势的 recipe 上局部打磨。选择 r27 而不是 r34/r18，是因为它提供了与 expert 路由最接近的 matched baseline，同时避免把结论混入 jumprelu 或大 K 主线。风险是该三段式原型在 K=192 处总成本大概率落在中成本带而非极低成本带，但这仍符合当前阶段允许用少量中成本质量锚点回答结构问题的策略。","next_hypotheses":["如果 `lowrank_expert_residual` 首轮能稳定训练且 FVU 明显优于 `expert_topk K=192`，下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `STAGE1_RATIO`，验证 expert 段与 residual 段的预算分配是否是主要控制旋钮。","如果该 family 训练稳定但收益有限，下一轮优先只改 `TRUNK_RANK`，验证 trunk 是否过重并侵蚀了低成本收益。","如果三段式 family 连 matched baseline 都无法明显改善，应停止继续围绕该原型打磨，转向 `two-stage residual expert` 方向，而不是回到 plain selector 家族。"],"notes_to_memory":["`lowrank_expert_residual` 的导出形式是 trunk 静态库 + 单 expert 静态子库 + residual 静态补偿库上的有限加权和，属于扩展兼容 family，不是动态字典。","本轮要回答的是三段式 `lowrank + expert + residual` 是否值得继续，而不是再问一次 `expert_topk` 或 `lowrank_expert_topk` 的 K 轴斜率。","建议实现时复用现有 lowrank trunk、expert local top-k、以及 residual second-pass 模块，避免新增 tunable 名称；优先复用现有 `TRUNK_RANK` 与 `STAGE1_RATIO` 语义。","若新增 family 需要后续调 `TRUNK_RANK`/`STAGE1_RATIO`，应同时补齐该 architecture 在 override registry 中的允许键，避免后续 param_only 回合静默拒绝 override。"],"touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py","research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py"]}
research/history/logs/agent_round_0044.stdout.log:697:research/history/logs/agent_action_0042.json:3:  "hypothesis": "最终重构公式设为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_{e(x-t(x))}(x-t(x))} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}，其中 t(x)=Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r。也就是先用静态 low-rank trunk 向量库 U={u_r} 重构平滑主干，再对残差用轻量 router 选择单个静态 expert 子库 B_e={b_{e,i}} 并做局部 sparse 修正；因此它可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“trunk 查表 + expert 子库查表 + 有限加权和”推理链路。兼容性判断：`lowrank_expert_topk` 属于扩展兼容。主假设是：相对 r27 的纯 `expert_topk`，加入轻量 low-rank trunk 后，能显著改善重构质量，并回答 `lowrank + expert` 这条高优先级结构线是否值得继续，即使首点落在中成本带也有信息价值。",
research/history/logs/agent_round_0044.stdout.log:698:research/history/logs/agent_action_0042.json:4:  "summary": "不回到 plain selector 邻域微调，也不继续对未知结果的 `two_stage_residual_expert` 做预设调参。本轮以 r27 的 `expert_topk K=192 EF=1` 为 matched baseline，只改 `ARCHITECTURE` 到 `lowrank_expert_topk`，先拿到 `lowrank + expert` 这条结构线在当前 target 上的首个真实训练点。",
research/history/logs/agent_round_0044.stdout.log:703:research/history/logs/agent_action_0042.json:24:    "如果 `lowrank_expert_topk` 首点明显优于 r27 `expert_topk`，下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `TRUNK_RANK` 向低成本方向压缩，测试是否能形成新的 Pareto 段。",
research/history/logs/agent_round_0044.stdout.log:722:research/history/logs/agent_round_0038.stdout.log:416:research/history/round_summaries/round_0037.json:28:    "summary": "\u4e0d\u7ee7\u7eed\u5728 `lowrank_expert_topk` \u4e0a\u505a\u7b2c\u4e09\u4e2a\u90bb\u57df\u626b\u70b9\uff0c\u800c\u662f\u8fdb\u5165\u4e0b\u4e00\u7ed3\u6784\u69fd\u4f4d\uff1a\u5b9e\u73b0\u6700\u5c0f\u53ef\u8fd0\u884c\u7684 `lowrank_expert_residual` \u539f\u578b\u3002\u4ee5 r27 \u7684 `expert_topk K=192 EF=1` \u4e3a matched baseline\uff0c\u53ea\u6539 `ARCHITECTURE`\uff0c\u5148\u9a8c\u8bc1\u4e09\u6bb5\u5f0f\u7ed3\u6784\u672c\u8eab\u662f\u5426\u503c\u5f97\u7ee7\u7eed\u3002",
research/history/logs/agent_round_0044.stdout.log:723:research/history/logs/agent_round_0038.stdout.log:424:research/history/round_summaries/round_0037.json:75:    "self_review": "\u8fd9\u6b21 repair \u6ca1\u6709\u6539 family_name\uff0c\u4e5f\u6ca1\u6709\u6539 env_overrides\uff1b\u4ecd\u7136\u662f\u76f8\u5bf9 r27 \u53ea\u5207\u6362\u5230 `ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_expert_residual`\u3002\u963b\u585e\u6839\u56e0\u662f `Unknown architecture`\uff0c\u5df2\u6309\u67b6\u6784\u96c6\u6210 checklist \u4fee\u590d\uff1awhitelist\u3001dispatch\u3001class\u3001exact-string smoke \u90fd\u5df2\u5b8c\u6210\u3002\u989d\u5916\u628a\u8be5 family \u63a5\u5230\u4e86 `TRUNK_RANK/STAGE1_RATIO` override registry\uff0c\u907f\u514d\u540e\u7eed\u8c03\u53c2\u65f6\u9759\u9ed8\u5931\u6548\u3002exact smoke \u5728 `lowrank_expert_residual, K=192, EF=1` \u4e0a\u901a\u8fc7\uff0c\u4f30\u7b97\u603b\u6210\u672c\u7ea6 1.06x \u539f\u59cb matmul\u3001\u9884\u7b97\u6bd4\u7387 0.71x\uff0c\u4ecd\u5728\u786c\u7ea6\u675f\u5185\u3002",
research/history/logs/agent_round_0044.stdout.log:726:research/history/logs/agent_round_0038.stdout.log:433:research/history/logs/agent_action_0037.json:1:{"change_type":"edit_sae_code","command":"run","family_name":"lowrank_expert_residual","family_stage":"prototype","reference_round":27,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_expert_residual"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","needs_sanity":true,"hypothesis":"最终重构公式设为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_e(x)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i} + Σ_{j∈T(x)} γ_j(x) c_j。这里 U={u_r} 是静态 low-rank trunk 向量库，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库，C={c_j} 是静态 residual 补偿库；在线侧先计算 trunk 系数 β_r(x)，再用轻量 router 选择单个 expert 子库 e(x) 并在其内做局部 sparse 选择，最后对剩余残差再做一次小预算 sparse 补偿。因此它仍可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”流水线，兼容性判定为扩展兼容。主假设是：在与 r27 相同的 EF=1、K=192 recipe 下，把 `expert_topk` 升级为 `lowrank + expert + residual` 三段式结构，能回答‘仅有 lowrank+expert 仍不足时，加入第二段 residual 修正是否会形成新的结构性 Pareto 段’这个当前更关键的问题。","summary":"不继续在 `lowrank_expert_topk` 上做第三个邻域扫点，而是进入下一结构槽位：实现最小可运行的 `lowrank_expert_residual` 原型。以 r27 的 `expert_topk K=192 EF=1` 为 matched baseline，只改 `ARCHITECTURE`，先验证三段式结构本身是否值得继续。","self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束：运行配置相对 r27 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。这轮优先解决结构未知量，而不是继续在已显示弱势的 recipe 上局部打磨。选择 r27 而不是 r34/r18，是因为它提供了与 expert 路由最接近的 matched baseline，同时避免把结论混入 jumprelu 或大 K 主线。风险是该三段式原型在 K=192 处总成本大概率落在中成本带而非极低成本带，但这仍符合当前阶段允许用少量中成本质量锚点回答结构问题的策略。","next_hypotheses":["如果 `lowrank_expert_residual` 首轮能稳定训练且 FVU 明显优于 `expert_topk K=192`，下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `STAGE1_RATIO`，验证 expert 段与 residual 段的预算分配是否是主要控制旋钮。","如果该 family 训练稳定但收益有限，下一轮优先只改 `TRUNK_RANK`，验证 trunk 是否过重并侵蚀了低成本收益。","如果三段式 family 连 matched baseline 都无法明显改善，应停止继续围绕该原型打磨，转向 `two-stage residual expert` 方向，而不是回到 plain selector 家族。"],"notes_to_memory":["`lowrank_expert_residual` 的导出形式是 trunk 静态库 + 单 expert 静态子库 + residual 静态补偿库上的有限加权和，属于扩展兼容 family，不是动态字典。","本轮要回答的是三段式 `lowrank + expert + residual` 是否值得继续，而不是再问一次 `expert_topk` 或 `lowrank_expert_topk` 的 K 轴斜率。","建议实现时复用现有 lowrank trunk、expert local top-k、以及 residual second-pass 模块，避免新增 tunable 名称；优先复用现有 `TRUNK_RANK` 与 `STAGE1_RATIO` 语义。","若新增 family 需要后续调 `TRUNK_RANK`/`STAGE1_RATIO`，应同时补齐该 architecture 在 override registry 中的允许键，避免后续 param_only 回合静默拒绝 override。"],"touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py","research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py"]}
research/history/logs/agent_round_0044.stdout.log:729:research/history/logs/agent_round_0038.stdout.log:446:research/history/logs/agent_round_0037_repair_1.stdout.log:1:{"change_type":"edit_sae_code","command":"run","family_name":"lowrank_expert_residual","family_stage":"prototype","reference_round":27,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_expert_residual"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","needs_sanity":true,"hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_e(x)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i} + Σ_{j∈T(x)} γ_j(x) c_j。这里 U={u_r} 是静态 low-rank trunk 向量库，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库，C={c_j} 是静态 residual 补偿库；在线侧先计算 trunk 系数 β_r(x)，再用轻量 router 选择单个 expert 子库 e(x) 并在其内做局部 sparse 选择，最后对剩余残差再做一次小预算 sparse 补偿。因此它仍可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”流水线，兼容性判定为扩展兼容。本次 repair 不改变实验设计，只修复 `lowrank_expert_residual` 的注册链与最小可运行实现，使原始 Round 37 实验能够按原设定重新运行。","summary":"已修复 Round 37 的工程性阻塞：补上 `lowrank_expert_residual` 的 config whitelist、factory dispatch、concrete class，并完成同一目标 `(ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_expert_residual, K=192, EF=1)` 的 instantiate/forward/backward smoke。保持原 family 与 env_overrides 不变，重新运行原始实验。","self_review":"这次 repair 没有改 family_name，也没有改 env_overrides；仍然是相对 r27 只切换到 `ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_expert_residual`。阻塞根因是 `Unknown architecture`，已按架构集成 checklist 修复：whitelist、dispatch、class、exact-string smoke 都已完成。额外把该 family 接到了 `TRUNK_RANK/STAGE1_RATIO` override registry，避免后续调参时静默失效。exact smoke 在 `lowrank_expert_residual, K=192, EF=1` 上通过，估算总成本约 1.06x 原始 matmul、预算比率 0.71x，仍在硬约束内。","next_hypotheses":["如果 rerun 能稳定完成，则再根据真实 FVU 判断 `lowrank + expert + residual` 是否值得继续；当前 repair 轮不对结构优劣做新结论。","如果 rerun 仍失败，下一次 repair 应直接针对新的失败模式处理，而不是再次回到注册链。"],"notes_to_memory":["Round 37 的首个 blocker 是注册链缺失，不是训练语义问题。","`lowrank_expert_residual` 已加入 `sparsify/config.py` whitelist，并加入 `sparsify/sparse_coder.py` dispatch。","已实现最小可运行 `LowRankExpertResidualSparseCoder`：low-rank trunk + expert-local first pass + global residual cleanup second pass。","已补 `research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py` 中 `lowrank_expert_residual -> {TRUNK_RANK, STAGE1_RATIO}`，避免后续 structural override 被拒绝。","exact smoke 结果：`integration_smoke: OK lowrank_expert_residual 192 1 cuda`；成本估算 combined_ratio≈1.06x，combined_budget_ratio≈0.71x，可行。"],"touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py","research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py"]}
