research/history/logs/agent_round_0044.stdout.log:1255:research/history/logs/agent_round_0037_repair_1.stdout.log:1999:{"change_type":"edit_sae_code","command":"run","family_name":"lowrank_expert_residual","family_stage":"prototype","reference_round":27,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_expert_residual"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","needs_sanity":true,"hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_e(x)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i} + Σ_{j∈T(x)} γ_j(x) c_j。这里 U={u_r} 是静态 low-rank trunk 向量库，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库，C={c_j} 是静态 residual 补偿库；在线侧先计算 trunk 系数 β_r(x)，再用轻量 router 选择单个 expert 子库 e(x) 并在其内做局部 sparse 选择，最后对剩余残差再做一次小预算 sparse 补偿。因此它仍可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”流水线，兼容性判定为扩展兼容。本次 repair 不改变实验设计，只修复 `lowrank_expert_residual` 的注册链与最小可运行实现，使原始 Round 37 实验能够按原设定重新运行。","summary":"已修复 Round 37 的工程性阻塞：补上 `lowrank_expert_residual` 的 config whitelist、factory dispatch、concrete class，并完成同一目标 `(ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_expert_residual, K=192, EF=1)` 的 instantiate/forward/backward smoke。保持原 family 与 env_overrides 不变，重新运行原始实验。","self_review":"这次 repair 没有改 family_name，也没有改 env_overrides；仍然是相对 r27 只切换到 `ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_expert_residual`。阻塞根因是 `Unknown architecture`，已按架构集成 checklist 修复：whitelist、dispatch、class、exact-string smoke 都已完成。额外把该 family 接到了 `TRUNK_RANK/STAGE1_RATIO` override registry，避免后续调参时静默失效。exact smoke 在 `lowrank_expert_residual, K=192, EF=1` 上通过，估算总成本约 1.06x 原始 matmul、预算比率 0.71x，仍在硬约束内。","next_hypotheses":["如果 rerun 能稳定完成，则再根据真实 FVU 判断 `lowrank + expert + residual` 是否值得继续；当前 repair 轮不对结构优劣做新结论。","如果 rerun 仍失败，下一次 repair 应直接针对新的失败模式处理，而不是再次回到注册链。"],"notes_to_memory":["Round 37 的首个 blocker 是注册链缺失，不是训练语义问题。","`lowrank_expert_residual` 已加入 `sparsify/config.py` whitelist，并加入 `sparsify/sparse_coder.py` dispatch。","已实现最小可运行 `LowRankExpertResidualSparseCoder`：low-rank trunk + expert-local first pass + global residual cleanup second pass。","已补 `research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py` 中 `lowrank_expert_residual -> {TRUNK_RANK, STAGE1_RATIO}`，避免后续 structural override 被拒绝。","exact smoke 结果：`integration_smoke: OK lowrank_expert_residual 192 1 cuda`；成本估算 combined_ratio≈1.06x，combined_budget_ratio≈0.71x，可行。"],"touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py","research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py"]}
research/history/logs/agent_round_0044.stdout.log:1357:research/history/logs/agent_round_0043.stdout.log:1:{"change_type":"edit_sae_code","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"TRUNK_RANK","value":"128"}],"expected_win":"lower_cost","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_expert_topk","family_stage":"stabilize","hypothesis":"最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_{e(x)}(x)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}。其中 U={u_r} 是静态 low-rank trunk 向量库，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库；在线侧先算 trunk 系数 β_r(x)，再用轻量 router 选单个 expert 子库 e(x)，并在该子库内做局部 top-k，因此可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”流水线。我将 `lowrank_expert_topk` 判定为扩展兼容。r42 已在默认 trunk_rank=384、K=192、EF=1 下得到 val_FVU≈0.0888，但总成本约 0.81x；主假设是把 `TRUNK_RANK` 单独降到 128 后，可把总成本压到约 0.44x，同时保留足够多的质量，从而在 <0.5x 带形成新的结构性 Pareto 段。由于这是该 family 首次把 `TRUNK_RANK` 接入 AutoResearch override 链路，本轮首先是参数生效确认轮，结果只有在 round*.config.json 与 checkpoint config.json 都出现 `TRUNK_RANK=128` 后才可作为结构证据。","needs_sanity":true,"next_hypotheses":["如果 `TRUNK_RANK=128` 生效且 FVU 仍明显优于当前 <0.5x anchor，则下一轮继续同 family，只改 `TRUNK_RANK=64`，测试 lowrank+expert 是否还能再向更低成本延伸。","如果 `TRUNK_RANK=128` 的质量退化过大，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `TRUNK_RANK=192`，寻找低成本与质量之间的折中点。","如果参数未真正进入训练配置或 checkpoint，则下一轮继续做接线修复，不对该 family 的质量做结论。"],"notes_to_memory":["`lowrank_expert_topk` 现已接入 `TRUNK_RANK` override 白名单；`validate_env_overrides` 对 `(ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_expert_topk, TRUNK_RANK=128)` 已通过。","兼容性注册表已补入 `lowrank_expert_topk`、`lowrank_expert_residual`、`two_stage_residual_expert`，三者均按 LUTurbo 导出约束标记为扩展兼容，避免新结构结果继续被 compatible frontier/prompt 过滤掉。","基于当前实现的成本估算，`lowrank_expert_topk K=192 EF=1 TRUNK_RANK=128` 的 total_cost 约为 0.44x，明显低于 r42 默认 trunk 的约 0.81x。"],"reference_round":42,"self_review":"本轮代码改动只做运行时 unblock：一是给 `lowrank_expert_topk` 打通 `TRUNK_RANK` override 白名单，二是把当前已实现的 expert/lowrank family 明确登记为扩展兼容。真正训练配置相对 r42 仍只改 1 个 env 参数：`TRUNK_RANK=128`。这满足单变量原则，也符合“先消除运行时/观测 blocker，再做结构判断”的优先级。风险在于本轮仍是首个接线验证轮，若只看到训练结果而不检查 round config/checkpoint config，就可能把无效 override 误判成结构结论。","summary":"先修复两个当前 blocker：`lowrank_expert_topk` 的 `TRUNK_RANK` override 接线，以及 lowrank+expert 系列在兼容性注册表中的缺失标注。随后基于 r42 只下调 `TRUNK_RANK` 到 128，做一个低成本验证轮，优先回答这条 lowrank+expert 结构能否把约 0.81x 的质量点压进 <0.5x 成本带。","touched_files":["research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py","research/AutoResearch/prior_research_history.md"]}
research/history/logs/agent_round_0044.stdout.log:1427:research/history/logs/agent_round_0043.stdout.log:2133:research/history/round_summaries/round_0037.json:75:    "self_review": "\u8fd9\u6b21 repair \u6ca1\u6709\u6539 family_name\uff0c\u4e5f\u6ca1\u6709\u6539 env_overrides\uff1b\u4ecd\u7136\u662f\u76f8\u5bf9 r27 \u53ea\u5207\u6362\u5230 `ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_expert_residual`\u3002\u963b\u585e\u6839\u56e0\u662f `Unknown architecture`\uff0c\u5df2\u6309\u67b6\u6784\u96c6\u6210 checklist \u4fee\u590d\uff1awhitelist\u3001dispatch\u3001class\u3001exact-string smoke \u90fd\u5df2\u5b8c\u6210\u3002\u989d\u5916\u628a\u8be5 family \u63a5\u5230\u4e86 `TRUNK_RANK/STAGE1_RATIO` override registry\uff0c\u907f\u514d\u540e\u7eed\u8c03\u53c2\u65f6\u9759\u9ed8\u5931\u6548\u3002exact smoke \u5728 `lowrank_expert_residual, K=192, EF=1` \u4e0a\u901a\u8fc7\uff0c\u4f30\u7b97\u603b\u6210\u672c\u7ea6 1.06x \u539f\u59cb matmul\u3001\u9884\u7b97\u6bd4\u7387 0.71x\uff0c\u4ecd\u5728\u786c\u7ea6\u675f\u5185\u3002",
