 expert` 方向本身。","summary":"已实现并 smoke 通过新的 `lowrank_expert_topk` family，用最小 lowrank+expert 原型覆盖当前高优先级未验证结构槽位。建议下一轮以 r12(topk K=128 EF=1) 为参考，只切换到 `ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_expert_topk`，先在约 0.56x total_cost 的低开销带验证该 family 是否能形成新的 Pareto 段。","touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py"]}
research/history/logs/agent_round_0044.stdout.log:1464:research/history/logs/agent_round_0043.stdout.log:2260:research/history/logs/agent_action_0040.json:1:{"change_type":"edit_sae_code","command":"run","family_name":"two_stage_residual_expert","family_stage":"prototype","reference_round":27,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"two_stage_residual_expert"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","needs_sanity":true,"hypothesis":"最终重构公式设为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_1(x)} α_i(x) b_i + Σ_{j∈S_{e(r_1)}(r_1)} γ_{e,j}(x) c_{e,j}，其中 r_1 = x - Σ_{i∈S_1(x)} α_i(x) b_i。第一段在静态 coarse library B={b_i} 上做有限加权和，第二段对剩余残差用轻量 router 选择一个静态 expert 子库 C_e={c_{e,j}} 并做局部 sparse 修正，因此它可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路，兼容性判定为扩展兼容。主假设是：相比已经很强但偏高成本的 `lowrank_expert_residual`，去掉 dense trunk，改为 `coarse sparse + expert residual` 两段式后，能在更低 total_cost 带形成新的结构性 Pareto 段，并直接回答 `two-stage residual expert` 是否值得继续。","summary":"不继续在 `lowrank_expert_residual` 上做第三轮局部调参，而是切到当前高优先级未充分验证方向 `two-stage residual expert`。以 r27 的 `expert_topk K=192 EF=1` 为 matched baseline，只改 `ARCHITECTURE`，先验证“coarse sparse + expert residual”这个新结构槽位本身是否成立。","self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束：运行配置相对 r27 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。当前已在 `lowrank_expert_residual` 上连续两轮未形成新前沿，更合理的下一步是扩大结构信息增量，而不是继续细扫其邻域。选择 `two_stage_residual_expert` 而不是再回到 plain selector，是因为它直接对应当前优先级列表中的未验证方向，同时比带 trunk 的三段式更有希望落入低到中成本带。","next_hypotheses":["如果 `two_stage_residual_expert` 首轮稳定且明显优于 `expert_topk K=192`，下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `STAGE1_RATIO`，验证 coarse 段与 expert residual 段的预算分配是否是主控制旋钮。","如果该 family 有信号但成本仍偏高，下一轮优先只改 `K` 或 `STAGE1_RATIO`，把它压向 0.3x-0.6x 带。","如果该原型仍不具竞争力，则说明当前 target 更可能需要 dense trunk；后续再回到 `lowrank_expert_residual` 的低成本化路线。"],"notes_to_memory":["`two_stage_residual_expert` 的导出形式是第一段静态 coarse library 加第二段单 expert 静态子库残差修正上的有限加权和，属于扩展兼容 family。","本轮优先回答新的结构问题，而不是继续在 `lowrank_expert_residual` 的 `TRUNK_RANK/STAGE1_RATIO` 上做局部扫点。","实现时应优先复用现有 `two_stage_residual` 与 `expert_topk` 组件，并复用已有 `STAGE1_RATIO` 语义，避免新增 tunable 名称。","若该新 family 需要后续调 `STAGE1_RATIO`，应在新增 family 时同步补齐 override registry 的允许键，避免后续 param_only 回合静默拒绝 override。"],"touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py","research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py"]}
research/history/logs/agent_round_0044.stdout.log:1469:research/history/logs/agent_round_0043.stdout.log:2272:research/history/logs/agent_round_0038.stdout.log:424:research/history/round_summaries/round_0037.json:75:    "self_review": "\u8fd9\u6b21 repair \u6ca1\u6709\u6539 family_name\uff0c\u4e5f\u6ca1\u6709\u6539 env_overrides\uff1b\u4ecd\u7136\u662f\u76f8\u5bf9 r27 \u53ea\u5207\u6362\u5230 `ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_expert_residual`\u3002\u963b\u585e\u6839\u56e0\u662f `Unknown architecture`\uff0c\u5df2\u6309\u67b6\u6784\u96c6\u6210 checklist \u4fee\u590d\uff1awhitelist\u3001dispatch\u3001class\u3001exact-string smoke \u90fd\u5df2\u5b8c\u6210\u3002\u989d\u5916\u628a\u8be5 family \u63a5\u5230\u4e86 `TRUNK_RANK/STAGE1_RATIO` override registry\uff0c\u907f\u514d\u540e\u7eed\u8c03\u53c2\u65f6\u9759\u9ed8\u5931\u6548\u3002exact smoke \u5728 `lowrank_expert_residual, K=192, EF=1` \u4e0a\u901a\u8fc7\uff0c\u4f30\u7b97\u603b\u6210\u672c\u7ea6 1.06x \u539f\u59cb matmul\u3001\u9884\u7b97\u6bd4\u7387 0.71x\uff0c\u4ecd\u5728\u786c\u7ea6\u675f\u5185\u3002",
research/history/logs/agent_round_0044.stdout.log:1471:research/history/logs/agent_round_0043.stdout.log:2275:research/history/logs/agent_round_0038.stdout.log:433:research/history/logs/agent_action_0037.json:1:{"change_type":"edit_sae_code","command":"run","family_name":"lowrank_expert_residual","family_stage":"prototype","reference_round":27,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_expert_residual"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","needs_sanity":true,"hypothesis":"最终重构公式设为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_e(x)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i} + Σ_{j∈T(x)} γ_j(x) c_j。这里 U={u_r} 是静态 low-rank trunk 向量库，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库，C={c_j} 是静态 residual 补偿库；在线侧先计算 trunk 系数 β_r(x)，再用轻量 router 选择单个 expert 子库 e(x) 并在其内做局部 sparse 选择，最后对剩余残差再做一次小预算 sparse 补偿。因此它仍可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”流水线，兼容性判定为扩展兼容。主假设是：在与 r27 相同的 EF=1、K=192 recipe 下，把 `expert_topk` 升级为 `lowrank + expert + residual` 三段式结构，能回答‘仅有 lowrank+expert 仍不足时，加入第二段 residual 修正是否会形成新的结构性 Pareto 段’这个当前更关键的问题。","summary":"不继续在 `lowrank_expert_topk` 上做第三个邻域扫点，而是进入下一结构槽位：实现最小可运行的 `lowrank_expert_residual` 原型。以 r27 的 `expert_topk K=192 EF=1` 为 matched baseline，只改 `ARCHITECTURE`，先验证三段式结构本身是否值得继续。","self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束：运行配置相对 r27 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。这轮优先解决结构未知量，而不是继续在已显示弱势的 recipe 上局部打磨。选择 r27 而不是 r34/r18，是因为它提供了与 expert 路由最接近的 matched baseline，同时避免把结论混入 jumprelu 或大 K 主线。风险是该三段式原型在 K=192 处总成本大概率落在中成本带而非极低成本带，但这仍符合当前阶段允许用少量中成本质量锚点回答结构问题的策略。","next_hypotheses":["如果 `lowrank_expert_residual` 首轮能稳定训练且 FVU 明显优于 `expert_topk K=192`，下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `STAGE1_RATIO`，验证 expert 段与 residual 段的预算分配是否是主要控制旋钮。","如果该 family 训练稳定但收益有限，下一轮优先只改 `TRUNK_RANK`，验证 trunk 是否过重并侵蚀了低成本收益。","如果三段式 family 连 matched baseline 都无法明显改善，应停止继续围绕该原型打磨，转向 `two-stage residual expert` 方向，而不是回到 plain selector 家族。"],"notes_to_memory":["`lowrank_expert_residual` 的导出形式是 trunk 静态库 + 单 expert 静态子库 + residual 静态补偿库上的有限加权和，属于扩展兼容 family，不是动态字典。","本轮要回答的是三段式 `lowrank + expert + residual` 是否值得继续，而不是再问一次 `expert_topk` 或 `lowrank_expert_topk` 的 K 轴斜率。","建议实现时复用现有 lowrank trunk、expert local top-k、以及 residual second-pass 模块，避免新增 tunable 名称；优先复用现有 `TRUNK_RANK` 与 `STAGE1_RATIO` 语义。","若新增 family 需要后续调 `TRUNK_RANK`/`STAGE1_RATIO`，应同时补齐该 architecture 在 override registry 中的允许键，避免后续 param_only 回合静默拒绝 override。"],"touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py","research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py"]}
research/history/logs/agent_round_0044.stdout.log:1473:research/history/logs/agent_round_0043.stdout.log:2278:research/history/logs/agent_round_0038.stdout.log:446:research/history/logs/agent_round_0037_repair_1.stdout.log:1:{"change_type":"edit_sae_code","command":"run","family_name":"lowrank_expert_residual","family_stage":"prototype","reference_round":27,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_expert_residual"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","needs_sanity":true,"hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_e(x)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i} + Σ_{j∈T(x)} γ_j(x) c_j。这里 U={u_r} 是静态 low-rank trunk 向量库，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库，C={c_j} 是静态 residual 补偿库；在线侧先计算 trunk 系数 β_r(x)，再用轻量 router 选择单个 expert 子库 e(x) 并在其内做局部 sparse 选择，最后对剩余残差再做一次小预算 sparse 补偿。因此它仍可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”流水线，兼容性判定为扩展兼容。本次 repair 不改变实验设计，只修复 `lowrank_expert_residual` 的注册链与最小可运行实现，使原始 Round 37 实验能够按原设定重新运行。","summary":"已修复 Round 37 的工程性阻塞：补上 `lowrank_expert_residual` 的 config whitelist、factory dispatch、concrete class，并完成同一目标 `(ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_expert_residual, K=192, EF=1)` 的 instantiate/forward/backward smoke。保持原 family 与 env_overrides 不变，重新运行原始实验。","self_review":"这次 repair 没有改 family_name，也没有改 env_overrides；仍然是相对 r27 只切换到 `ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_expert_residual`。阻塞根因是 `Unknown architecture`，已按架构集成 checklist 修复：whitelist、dispatch、class、exact-string smoke 都已完成。额外把该 family 接到了 `TRUNK_RANK/STAGE1_RATIO` override registry，避免后续调参时静默失效。exact smoke 在 `lowrank_expert_residual, K=192, EF=1` 上通过，估算总成本约 1.06x 原始 matmul、预算比率 0.71x，仍在硬约束内。","next_hypotheses":["如果 rerun 能稳定完成，则再根据真实 FVU 判断 `lowrank + expert + residual` 是否值得继续；当前 repair 轮不对结构优劣做新结论。","如果 rerun 仍失败，下一次 repair 应直接针对新的失败模式处理，而不是再次回到注册链。"],"notes_to_memory":["Round 37 的首个 blocker 是注册链缺失，不是训练语义问题。","`lowrank_expert_residual` 已加入 `sparsify/config.py` whitelist，并加入 `sparsify/sparse_coder.py` dispatch。","已实现最小可运行 `LowRankExpertResidualSparseCoder`：low-rank trunk + expert-local first pass + global residual cleanup second pass。","已补 `research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py` 中 `lowrank_expert_residual -> {TRUNK_RANK, STAGE1_RATIO}`，避免后续 structural override 被拒绝。","exact smoke 结果：`integration_smoke: OK lowrank_expert_residual 192 1 cuda`；成本估算 combined_ratio≈1.06x，combined_budget_ratio≈0.71x，可行。"],"touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py","research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py"]}
