expert` 方向本身。","summary":"已实现并 smoke 通过新的 `lowrank_expert_topk` family，用最小 lowrank+expert 原型覆盖当前高优先级未验证结构槽位。建议下一轮以 r12(topk K=128 EF=1) 为参考，只切换到 `ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_expert_topk`，先在约 0.56x total_cost 的低开销带验证该 family 是否能形成新的 Pareto 段。","touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py"]}
research/history/logs/agent_round_0050.stdout.log:1180:research/history/logs/agent_round_0044.stdout.log:1021:research/history/logs/agent_round_0042.stdout.log:3:  "hypothesis": "最终重构公式设为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_{e(x-t(x))}(x-t(x))} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}，其中 t(x)=Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r。也就是先用静态 low-rank trunk 向量库 U={u_r} 重构平滑主干，再对残差用轻量 router 选择单个静态 expert 子库 B_e={b_{e,i}} 并做局部 sparse 修正；因此它可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“trunk 查表 + expert 子库查表 + 有限加权和”推理链路。兼容性判断：`lowrank_expert_topk` 属于扩展兼容。主假设是：相对 r27 的纯 `expert_topk`，加入轻量 low-rank trunk 后，能显著改善重构质量，并回答 `lowrank + expert` 这条高优先级结构线是否值得继续，即使首点落在中成本带也有信息价值。",
research/history/logs/agent_round_0050.stdout.log:1181:research/history/logs/agent_round_0044.stdout.log:1022:research/history/logs/agent_round_0042.stdout.log:4:  "summary": "不回到 plain selector 邻域微调，也不继续对未知结果的 `two_stage_residual_expert` 做预设调参。本轮以 r27 的 `expert_topk K=192 EF=1` 为 matched baseline，只改 `ARCHITECTURE` 到 `lowrank_expert_topk`，先拿到 `lowrank + expert` 这条结构线在当前 target 上的首个真实训练点。",
research/history/logs/agent_round_0050.stdout.log:1185:research/history/logs/agent_round_0044.stdout.log:1027:research/history/logs/agent_round_0042.stdout.log:24:    "如果 `lowrank_expert_topk` 首点明显优于 r27 `expert_topk`，下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `TRUNK_RANK` 向低成本方向压缩，测试是否能形成新的 Pareto 段。",
