research/history/logs/agent_round_0050.stdout.log:1187:research/history/logs/agent_round_0044.stdout.log:1034:research/history/logs/agent_round_0042.stdout.log:420:  "summary": "不回到 plain selector 邻域微调，也不继续对未知结果的 `two_stage_residual_expert` 做预设调参。本轮以 r27 的 `expert_topk K=192 EF=1` 为 matched baseline，只改 `ARCHITECTURE` 到 `lowrank_expert_topk`，先拿到 `lowrank + expert` 这条结构线在当前 target 上的首个真实训练点。",
