是否值得继续，而不是再问一次 `expert_topk` 或 `lowrank_expert_topk` 的 K 轴斜率。","建议实现时复用现有 lowrank trunk、expert local top-k、以及 residual second-pass 模块，避免新增 tunable 名称；优先复用现有 `TRUNK_RANK` 与 `STAGE1_RATIO` 语义。","若新增 family 需要后续调 `TRUNK_RANK`/`STAGE1_RATIO`，应同时补齐该 architecture 在 override registry 中的允许键，避免后续 param_only 回合静默拒绝 override。"],"touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py","research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py"]}
research/history/logs/agent_round_0050.stdout.log:1939:research/history/logs/agent_round_0049.stdout.log:1609:research/history/logs/agent_round_0044.stdout.log:780:research/history/logs/agent_action_0043.json:1:{"change_type":"edit_sae_code","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"TRUNK_RANK","value":"128"}],"expected_win":"lower_cost","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_expert_topk","family_stage":"stabilize","hypothesis":"最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_{e(x)}(x)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}。其中 U={u_r} 是静态 low-rank trunk 向量库，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库；在线侧先算 trunk 系数 β_r(x)，再用轻量 router 选单个 expert 子库 e(x)，并在该子库内做局部 top-k，因此可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”流水线。我将 `lowrank_expert_topk` 判定为扩展兼容。r42 已在默认 trunk_rank=384、K=192、EF=1 下得到 val_FVU≈0.0888，但总成本约 0.81x；主假设是把 `TRUNK_RANK` 单独降到 128 后，可把总成本压到约 0.44x，同时保留足够多的质量，从而在 <0.5x 带形成新的结构性 Pareto 段。由于这是该 family 首次把 `TRUNK_RANK` 接入 AutoResearch override 链路，本轮首先是参数生效确认轮，结果只有在 round*.config.json 与 checkpoint config.json 都出现 `TRUNK_RANK=128` 后才可作为结构证据。","needs_sanity":true,"next_hypotheses":["如果 `TRUNK_RANK=128` 生效且 FVU 仍明显优于当前 <0.5x anchor，则下一轮继续同 family，只改 `TRUNK_RANK=64`，测试 lowrank+expert 是否还能再向更低成本延伸。","如果 `TRUNK_RANK=128` 的质量退化过大，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `TRUNK_RANK=192`，寻找低成本与质量之间的折中点。","如果参数未真正进入训练配置或 checkpoint，则下一轮继续做接线修复，不对该 family 的质量做结论。"],"notes_to_memory":["`lowrank_expert_topk` 现已接入 `TRUNK_RANK` override 白名单；`validate_env_overrides` 对 `(ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_expert_topk, TRUNK_RANK=128)` 已通过。","兼容性注册表已补入 `lowrank_expert_topk`、`lowrank_expert_residual`、`two_stage_residual_expert`，三者均按 LUTurbo 导出约束标记为扩展兼容，避免新结构结果继续被 compatible frontier/prompt 过滤掉。","基于当前实现的成本估算，`lowrank_expert_topk K=192 EF=1 TRUNK_RANK=128` 的 total_cost 约为 0.44x，明显低于 r42 默认 trunk 的约 0.81x。"],"reference_round":42,"self_review":"本轮代码改动只做运行时 unblock：一是给 `lowrank_expert_topk` 打通 `TRUNK_RANK` override 白名单，二是把当前已实现的 expert/lowrank family 明确登记为扩展兼容。真正训练配置相对 r42 仍只改 1 个 env 参数：`TRUNK_RANK=128`。这满足单变量原则，也符合“先消除运行时/观测 blocker，再做结构判断”的优先级。风险在于本轮仍是首个接线验证轮，若只看到训练结果而不检查 round config/checkpoint config，就可能把无效 override 误判成结构结论。","summary":"先修复两个当前 blocker：`lowrank_expert_topk` 的 `TRUNK_RANK` override 接线，以及 lowrank+expert 系列在兼容性注册表中的缺失标注。随后基于 r42 只下调 `TRUNK_RANK` 到 128，做一个低成本验证轮，优先回答这条 lowrank+expert 结构能否把约 0.81x 的质量点压进 <0.5x 成本带。","touched_files":["research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py","research/AutoResearch/prior_research_history.md"]}
research/history/logs/agent_round_0050.stdout.log:1940:research/history/logs/agent_round_0049.stdout.log:1610:research/history/logs/agent_round_0044.stdout.log:828:research/history/logs/agent_round_0039.stdout.log:421:    "summary": "\u4e0d\u7ee7\u7eed\u5728 `lowrank_expert_topk` \u4e0a\u505a\u7b2c\u4e09\u4e2a\u90bb\u57df\u626b\u70b9\uff0c\u800c\u662f\u8fdb\u5165\u4e0b\u4e00\u7ed3\u6784\u69fd\u4f4d\uff1a\u5b9e\u73b0\u6700\u5c0f\u53ef\u8fd0\u884c\u7684 `lowrank_expert_residual` \u539f\u578b\u3002\u4ee5 r27 \u7684 `expert_topk K=192 EF=1` \u4e3a matched baseline\uff0c\u53ea\u6539 `ARCHITECTURE`\uff0c\u5148\u9a8c\u8bc1\u4e09\u6bb5\u5f0f\u7ed3\u6784\u672c\u8eab\u662f\u5426\u503c\u5f97\u7ee7\u7eed\u3002",
research/history/logs/agent_round_0050.stdout.log:1946:research/history/logs/agent_round_0049.stdout.log:1616:research/history/logs/agent_round_0044.stdout.log:856:research/history/logs/agent_round_0035.stdout.log:1:{"change_type":"edit_sae_code","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_expert_topk"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","experiment_tier":"proxy","family_name":"lowrank_expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_{e(x)}(x)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}。其中 U={u_r} 是静态 low-rank trunk 库，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库；在线侧先算 trunk 系数 β_r(x)，再用轻量 router 选择一个静态 expert 子库 e(x)，并只在该子库内做 local top-k 得到 α_{e,i}(x)。因此它可直接导出到 LUTurbo 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”链路，兼容性判定为扩展兼容。主假设：在 EF=1、K=128 的低开销带，lowrank trunk 先吸收平滑主干、expert local top-k 再处理残差，能比 plain expert_topk 与同带宽 plain selector 提供更好的 FVU/total_cost 权衡，并形成新的 Pareto 段。","needs_sanity":true,"next_hypotheses":["如果 r12->lowrank_expert_topk(K=128) 给出有效信号且 FVU 明显优于当前 0.38x-0.56x 邻域锚点，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 K 到 160，验证该 family 在 0.69x total_cost 处是否继续沿 Pareto 前进。","如果该原型训练不稳或收益不足，则优先继续实现 `lowrank + expert + residual`，而不是回到 plain topk/jumprelu 的局部扫点。"],"notes_to_memory":["已按 sae-architecture-integration checklist 完成新 family 接线：`lowrank_expert_topk` 已加入 `sparsify/config.py` whitelist，并加入 `sparsify/sparse_coder.py` dispatch。","新增原型 family 的导出形式为 trunk 静态库 + 单 expert 静态子库上的有限加权和，满足 LUTurbo 静态库约束，兼容性应视为扩展兼容。","已完成 instantiate/forward/backward smoke：`lowrank_expert_topk`, K=128, EF=1 通过。","当前原型采用固定 4 experts、active_experts=1、无新增 tunable 参数，因此本轮只需改 `ARCHITECTURE`，不需要修改 `research/AutoResearch/` 或 `scripts/autoresearch_test.sh`。","在 target proxy(1024x4096) 上，`lowrank_expert_topk` 的估算成本为：K=128 -> total 0.56x；K=160 -> total 0.69x；K=192 -> total 0.81x。低开销起点应优先从 K=128 开始。"],"reference_round":12,"self_review":"这轮只改了一个 env 参数 `ARCHITECTURE`，相对 r12 保持 K=128、EF=1、LR=8e-4、optimizer=adam 不变，归因清晰。代码侧只做最小 family 原型接线，没有引入新 tunable，因此不存在 override/runner 静默回退风险。风险是当前 prototype 的 expert 数和 active_experts 仍是固定值，若首轮效果一般，不能立刻下结论否定 `lowrank + expert` 方向本身。","summary":"已实现并 smoke 通过新的 `lowrank_expert_topk` family，用最小 lowrank+expert 原型覆盖当前高优先级未验证结构槽位。建议下一轮以 r12(topk K=128 EF=1) 为参考，只切换到 `ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_expert_topk`，先在约 0.56x total_cost 的低开销带验证该 family 是否能形成新的 Pareto 段。","touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py"]}
